<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 I'll praise you, Lord, with all my heart
 Before the gods - I'll sing - your praise
 I will bow down and praise your name
 For all your love and your faithfulness
 For though walk, in the midst of trouble
 You preserve my life
 You stretch your hand against
 The anger of my foes
 And with your right hand you same me lord
 The Lord will vindicate me
 Your love, O Lord, endures forever
 The Lord fulfills his purpose for me

